#. Description of the plugin
#: trece-withdrawal-eu.php
msgid "This plugin provides tools to help implement EU withdrawal rights. It does not constitute legal advice. Please consult a qualified legal professional to ensure full compliance with applicable regulations."
msgstr "Este plugin proporciona herramientas para ayudar a implementar los derechos de desistimiento de la UE. No constituye asesoramiento legal. Consulte a un profesional jurídico cualificado para garantizar el pleno cumplimiento de la normativa aplicable."

